Miss Vietnam World 2010 nominated for Miss Earth
VietNamNet Bridge – Luu Thi Diem Huong is waiting for the Ministry of Culture, Sports and Tourism’s licence to become Vietnam’s contestant at the Miss Earth pageant, which will take place in Nha Trang this November.
The Miss Earth 2010 pageant will be held from November 4 to December 4 in HCM City, Phan Thiet, Hoi An and Nha Trang.
Around 90 international beauties will arrive in HCM City on November 4 to participate in the first events. The final night will be held in Nha Trang on December 4.
Diem Huong met with Miss Earth 2008 Karla Henry, Miss Earth 2009 Larissa Ramos and Miss Philippines Earth 2010 Psyche Resus on October 16 in HCM City.
The four beauty queens will visit Phan Thiet, Binh Thuan, Nha Trang and Phu Yen from October 17-22.
